title: WHITEPAPER
body:
The simple idea is that some volunteers in the group with the info received from Tim Templeton make a whitepaper regarding the project and the website that Tim. Whitepaper must include the general idea, milestone to accomplish, and periods of time to do so. It could make it easier to explain the project to NEW INVESTORS.*

I know that making a good whitepaper is work so I suggest paying for it through part of the tx fees.

Tim is all-around programming for the website so he probably can't do it what do you think?
choices: yes but whitepaper must be done for free
author: 0x97f4319bfEFd1394fC33E0721cBe7388C57Aa810
